<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.FemBoyGamerTechGuy.NovaDream</id>
  <name>NovaDream</name>
  <summary>A dreamy multi-store game launcher</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      NovaDream is a native Linux game launcher with multi-store support.
      It supports local games, Steam, Epic Games, GOG, and Itch.io libraries,
      with Wine and Proton-GE runner management built in.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Launch Windows games via Wine or Proton-GE/UMU</li>
      <li>Multi-store library (Steam, Epic, GOG, Itch.io, Local)</li>
      <li>Per-game runner, prefix, and launch configuration</li>
      <li>Wine-Wayland native rendering support</li>
      <li>MangoHud and GameMode integration</li>
      <li>System tray support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
